name: Insert Into
func:
var query

switch (msg.wmode){
    case 0 :
        query = "INSERT INTO request (mode,X1,Y1,Z1) VALUES ('Zero',0000,0000,0000);"
        break
    case 1:
        var x=msg.payload[1]
        var y=msg.payload[2]
        var z=msg.payload[3]
        query ="INSERT INTO request (mode,X1,Y1,Z1) VALUES ('Position',"+x+","+y+","+z+");"
        break
    case 2:
        var xi=msg.payload[1]
        var yi=msg.payload[2]
        var zi=msg.payload[3]
        var xf=msg.payload[4]
        var yf=msg.payload[5]
        var zf=msg.payload[6]
        var n=msg.payload[7]
        query = "INSERT INTO request (mode,X1,Y1,Z1,X2,Y2,Z2,cicles) VALUES ('Auto',"+xi+","+yi+","+zi+","+xf+","+yf+","+zf+","+n+");"
        break
}

msg.topic=query;
return msg;
